{
  "stem": "2833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was me because you have no idea how you look when you are all of a sudden without hair.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so then we were, as I say, in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And every day we were counted a few times for hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we were-- there was selection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we-- the thing was that we had kapos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Those are the-- they were mostly older than we were, longer in camp, and kind of hardened and nasty and vicious women.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they had a stick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Each one had some kind of a stick in their hand that that was a sign of their power and of their station, which was above ours.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one day I was standing in the, in the selection [SIGHS] and not knowing really what it is yet, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when they selected girls, the others had to make a, a ring around and hold hands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were not allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was in there-- the last one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I saw that stick on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't know till today what made me do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I just bent down, picked it up, and walked out into the circle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this is how I got out of one selection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I never got selected again, thank God.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But somehow-- I don't know-- guardian angel, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had so many guardian angels through those years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I got back into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then one day, [SIGHS] we were told to come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were going to a factory, airplane factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was near Dresden in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there we were taken in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I think we were 75 in one cattle car.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
